In re KBB and KAB. No. 179P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2005. Richard E. Jester, for Shannon Tomica Burkes.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 6th day of April 2005 by Petitioner (Guilford County Dept. of Social Services) to Dismiss Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference this the 4th day of May 2005."
